{"tid":364850,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［健康台］鼻腔入面有鼻涕黏住點搞好","createTime":"2017-08-18T17:35:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T04:13:08.000Z","uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"170e60faa118b955269cd9cec42d6140e4341039","tid":364850,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:35:25.000Z","msg":"呢排一直有呢個問題 啲鼻涕塞住係鼻腔入面 feel到係喉嚨上少少個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好唔舒服 持續左一個月左右 窮撚唔捨得睇醫生 諗住等佢自然好 點知好左一排 又有返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但可以用鼻透氣 無鼻塞 無喉嚨痛 係咪鼻炎？<br />\n想枝針筒試下洗鼻 但覺得洗鼻好似洗唔到我舊鼻涕個個位..<br />\n<br />\n有無巴絲有同樣情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edeb198e2c763355f92eb502875163b4b7851565","tid":364850,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:40:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6cf8083f0a561a91ed6a6d499e0674e42bcbe092","tid":364850,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:42:38.000Z","msg":"吸落喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"e5b8c3315a9cebed00a641986f11e19e8cd7cd9d","tid":364850,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:43:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>吸落喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n試過好大力索。索極都索唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f05ea99efdefdf140ef76812846612a3e2b16cb","tid":364850,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:45:24.000Z","msg":"用鹽水洗下鼻，有隻係好似gas咁罐裝，有得隊入個鼻到洗<br />\n但唔知出面買幾錢<br />\n我諗係鼻水倒流加上比較杰身所以塞住<br />\n但我都係覺得你睇下醫生好d<br />\n利申有鼻敏感"},{"pid":"48a1b833a5fdd3346cd120bc92e2fe1026a8a805","tid":364850,"uid":35081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:45:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>吸落喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n試過好大力索。索極都索唔到落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁用針筒洗鼻啦<br />\n用暖水+少少鹽溝埋"},{"pid":"837355e540ae8ec93f89033d0d966ebbf4e45dfe","tid":364850,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:49:13.000Z","msg":"買針筒好似平啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 聽日去買先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁如果針筒洗鼻 應該吱左定右鼻窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> feel到舊鼻涕塞係靠左嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9278098a485725dee15cbfc6fc828e8dbfcd3b13","tid":364850,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:59:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"47b3a1db1c0aa9008c4e7d3a0c278cc02bcf890b","tid":364850,"uid":97162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T18:56:18.000Z","msg":"有冇試過沖涼個時呻<br />\n我鼻敏感朝朝起身都會塞住好大篤係鼻<br />\n沖涼個時可能因為蒸氣軟化左<br />\n好易呻得出"},{"pid":"dc7349d3e0de38e74c209613a7630636b8174fc8","tid":364850,"uid":51890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:09:14.000Z","msg":"我都係，瞓到半夜個鼻腔乾得濟，仲塞得緊要，結果成晩係到filifele，教都瞓唔好，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2a5147ba5f1c3d0df737a50b7e7cc31929526f","tid":364850,"uid":36993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T19:16:33.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感嘅大家食藥啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一蚊一粒，每晚大覺訓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58eee6ce5d0c9344a99122504ac5f944779ee6ff","tid":364850,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇試過沖涼個時呻<br />\n我鼻敏感朝朝起身都會塞住好大篤係鼻<br />\n沖涼個時可能因為蒸氣軟化左<br />\n好易呻得出</blockquote><br />\n試下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a919106d2e269ff82d7dcb73eea559fe20cfcc1c","tid":364850,"uid":53663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-19T04:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係，瞓到半夜個鼻腔乾得濟，仲塞得緊要，結果成晩係到filifele，教都瞓唔好，好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唉 失左成晚眠...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}